MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2014-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 29th January, 2014
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 28th January, 2014:
(i) Kumari Selja relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Social Justice and
Empowerment; and
(ii) Shri Mallikarjun Kharge, Minister of Railways assumed the additional charge of the office of
the Minister of Social Justice and Empowerment.
